CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 9, 1957, pg. A1 reads: "Page One Winners - Selected by the staffs of their respective newspapers for consistently superior work throughout 1956, each member in above group picture was honored with the Pittsburgh newspaper, Guild's editorial award at the fifth annual Page One Ball. Reading from left to right; William G. Nunn Jr., Courier sportswriter; Frank Ramsden, New Kensington Dispatch reporter; Zoara Unkovich, Sun-Telegraph reporter; Joseph E. Brown, Sun-Telegraph assistant news editor; James Bender, Post Gazette copy reader; Charles H. Allard, Post-Gazette labor editor. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait, left to right: William G. Nunn Jr., Frank Ramsden, Zoara Unkovich, Joseph E. Brown, James Bender, and Charles H. Allard, received Pittsburgh Newspaper Guild's editorial awards, standing in interior
